<paragraph id="8BA4CB2DFFF8FFC2FCABF88FFE357439" blockId="4.[811,1458,1779,2028]" lastBlockId="6.[132,775,216,338]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="119" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">
<bibRefCitation id="EF8AB6DCFFF8FFC0FCABF88FFBE57244" author="LECOMTE H." box="[813,1039,1810,1837]" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" pagination="915 - 978" refId="ref13275" refString="LECOMTE H. 1930. - Ebenacees, in LECOMTE H. &amp; HUMBERT H. (eds), Flore generale de l'Indo-Chine. Vol. 3. Masson &amp; Co., Paris: 915 - 978. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 27563332" type="book chapter" year="1930">Lecomte (1930: 941)</bibRefCitation>
cited collections of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FB58F88EFAC07244" box="[1246,1322,1810,1836]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Poilane</emphasis>
from “ 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FAF3F88EFA467244" box="[1397,1452,1810,1836]" name="Laos" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Laos</collectingCountry>
: vallée de la Tché-pone” and 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FBD1F8AEFB4A7224" box="[1111,1184,1842,1868]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Béjaud</emphasis>
from “Cambodge” as the original gathering. Three sheets of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FB2BF8CEFAA37204" box="[1197,1353,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Poilane 13333</emphasis>
collected from Tchépone have been located at 
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF8FFC0FB42F8EEFB3972E4" box="[1220,1235,1906,1932]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
and 
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF8FFC0FA8AF8EEFAA472E4" box="[1292,1358,1906,1932]" country="Viet Nam" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/tj07-dt2h" name="Institute of Tropical Biology" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="Herbarium">VNM</collectionCode>
and one sheet of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FC0DF80EFBED72C4" box="[907,1031,1938,1964]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Béjaud 212</emphasis>
from 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FBCBF80EFB5472C4" box="[1101,1214,1938,1964]" name="Cambodia" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
has been located at 
<collectorName id="26EEAEFBFFF8FFC0FA19F80EFCBD72A4" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF8FFC0FA19F80EFA4772C4" box="[1439,1453,1938,1964]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
. The
</collectorName>
locality on the label of 
<emphasis id="B96F173FFFF8FFC0FBDDF82EFB1C72A4" box="[1115,1270,1970,1996]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Poilane 13333</emphasis>
(
<collectionCode id="ED0A53E8FFF8FFC0FA80F82EFAFD72A4" box="[1286,1303,1970,1996]" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="Herbarium">P</collectionCode>
[
<specimenCode id="DBBD6356FFF8FFC0FA98F82EFA7772A4" box="[1310,1437,1970,1996]" collectionCode="P" country="France" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15763" name="Museum National d' Histoire Naturelle, Paris (MNHN) - Vascular Plants" pageId="4" pageNumber="117" type="Herbarium">P00721642</specimenCode>
]) indicated that Tchépone was in 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FB09F84EFB357284" box="[1167,1247,2002,2028]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Annam</collectingCountry>
(central 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFF8FFC0FAC4F84DFA4F7284" box="[1346,1445,2001,2028]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="117">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
). 
<location id="8EC49DF6FFFAFFC2FF02FF44FEEB759A" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03B27A3BFFF8FFC2FCD5FAE8FE357439:8EC49DF6FFFAFFC2FF02FF44FEEB759A" box="[132,257,216,242]" country="Laos" county="It" municipality="Poilane" name="This village" pageId="6" pageNumber="119">This village</location>
is, in fact, in 
<collectingCountry id="F30C8BBDFFFAFFC2FE27FF44FE3C759A" box="[417,470,216,242]" name="Laos" pageId="6" pageNumber="119">Laos</collectingCountry>
, close to the Laos-Vietnam border. The specimen 
